1
00:01:30,970 --> 00:01:35,060
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,150 --> 00:01:35,680
Xiaolan.

3
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,120
The Xiangsheng cuisine here
is very authentic.

4
00:01:35,789 --> 00:01:39,229
[2010]

5
00:01:37,150 --> 00:01:38,120
Try it out

6
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:38,870
today.

7
00:01:39,070 --> 00:01:39,430
Okay.

8
00:01:41,479 --> 00:01:42,229
Mr. Chen?

9
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,400
-Li.
-Hello, Mr. Chen.

10
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:44,930
Xiaolan.

11
00:01:45,350 --> 00:01:46,680
You like spicy food too?

12
00:01:46,870 --> 00:01:48,070
I'm from Xiangsheng.

13
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:49,280
Of course I love spicy food.

14
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:49,680
I see.

15
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,770
Enjoy your meal.

16
00:01:50,789 --> 00:01:51,120
Okay.

17
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:52,810
Xiaolan!

18
00:01:53,229 --> 00:01:53,920
Come here.

19
00:01:53,950 --> 00:01:55,410
Let me have a word with you.

20
00:01:58,789 --> 00:01:59,870
With your education,

21
00:01:59,870 --> 00:02:00,760
it's your good fortune

22
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,220
that you can get into Luna.

23
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,700
You must work hard and learn well.

24
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:06,790
These are the best years of your life.

25
00:02:06,790 --> 00:02:08,110
I have high hopes for you.

26
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:09,120
Thank you, Mr. Chen.

27
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:09,680
All right.

28
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:10,750
Go and have your meal.

29
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:11,080
Okay.

30
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:12,150
Enjoy your meal.

31
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:17,870
Hello, what would you like to order?

32
00:02:17,990 --> 00:02:20,700
[Episode 14: The Best Years]

33
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,490
What's going on?

34
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,220
Something has been off since yesterday.

35
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:28,590
Maybe things

36
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,010
happened too suddenly,

37
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:31,140
and I got startled.

38
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:33,560
You don't look like someone

39
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,020
who gets startled easily.

40
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,430
There's just been
too much going on lately.

41
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:40,960
I'm probably just too tense and tired.

42
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,360
This is a good opportunity

43
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,560
to take a break.

44
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,220
I'm glad you know that.

45
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,630
Since you came to Shengcheng,

46
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:48,030
you haven't had
a single day of proper rest.

47
00:02:55,190 --> 00:02:56,800
Shumai, barbecue pork bun.

48
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:59,079
Barbecue pork bun.

49
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:00,240
Do you want some?

50
00:03:00,710 --> 00:03:01,120
Yes.

51
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:08,250
[Gangdao]

52
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:10,520
Young Master.

53
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:12,000
Your new teeth look nice.

54
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,200
What are you laughing at?

55
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,750
Is Xia Dajun

56
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,320
still at the company?

57
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,430
Xia Dajun?

58
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:22,720
He's basically illiterate.

59
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,720
He couldn't do

60
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:24,870
anything right in the office.

61
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:26,360
He was fired last month.

62
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,079
That loser.

63
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,630
He's even more useless than I imagined.

64
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:31,630
How could Xia Xiaolan have

65
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:32,690
a father like that?

66
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,590
Get someone to keep an eye on him.

67
00:03:35,590 --> 00:03:37,910
Also find a chance to tell him

68
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:40,560
that Xia Xiaolan is also in Shengcheng.

69
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:42,630
Doesn't Miss Xia

70
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:44,160
want nothing to do with him?

71
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,960
That's why she needs to have something
to do with him.

72
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,250
They are father and daughter, after all.

73
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:48,980
You are so smart, Young Master.

74
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:52,710
Can a family like that Jerk Zhou's

75
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:53,560
accept Xia Xiaolan

76
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,020
having a father like this?

77
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:00,800
Hello?

78
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,240
Daddy!

79
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:04,710
Yes.

80
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,030
I'm going to go discuss a contract.

81
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:06,830
I'm very busy.

82
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,760
Your second brother is busy with work,
and so are you.

83
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,530
When will

84
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,490
you two brothers

85
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,680
sit down and have a meal with me

86
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,910
to have a chat?

87
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,610
Perfect timing.

88
00:04:16,950 --> 00:04:18,190
It's still early.

89
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,190
Zhaoji should be at the company, right?

90
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:22,320
I'll go pick him up to go home together.

91
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,560
Change the route.

92
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,360
Go to the Group.

93
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:29,950
Okay.

94
00:04:39,730 --> 00:04:41,640
[Chengrong Group]

95
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:40,920
Hello, Elder Young Master.

96
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,450
Hello, Elder Young Master.

97
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:48,430
The Second Young Master is in a meeting.

98
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:49,680
Don't you recognize me?

99
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,750
You are the Elder Young Master.

100
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:51,830
I've seen your photo

101
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:53,030
in the Group's files.

102
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:54,930
And you still dare to block me?

103
00:04:55,950 --> 00:04:57,630
Where did Zhaoji find such a

104
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,870
loyal,

105
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,160
clueless Mainland girl?

106
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:04,780
Xiaoqiong!

107
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:07,870
Second Young Master.

108
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:09,000
This is my big brother.

109
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,190
We are all Du family members.

110
00:05:10,190 --> 00:05:12,390
Big Brother can come whenever he wants.

111
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:17,500
Big Brother, your injury...

112
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:19,480
The old man said
you're under a lot of pressure.

113
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:21,480
He wanted me to pick you up from work.

114
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:24,040
Your secretary is so fierce.

115
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,950
You should just

116
00:05:26,690 --> 00:05:27,350
fire her.

117
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:31,800
Just kidding.

118
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:32,830
Relax.

119
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,830
My car has been parked downstairs
for a while now.

120
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:36,800
If we don't go down soon,

121
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,330
the police will tow it away.

122
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:40,290
I'll be right there.

123
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,480
Come. A toast to the family.

124
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,120
Dear.

125
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,040
Zhaoji,

126
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,480
you must remember,

127
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,630
Work is work,

128
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,260
but you must watch your health.

129
00:06:03,260 --> 00:06:05,410
Don't be a workaholic like your Daddy.

130
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,290
Understand?

131
00:06:06,870 --> 00:06:07,680
I know, Mommy.

132
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,010
Good boy.

133
00:06:09,310 --> 00:06:10,800
The Second Young Master works hard.

134
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,270
But the Elder Young Master
must be working very hard

135
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:13,510
to open up the market in the Mainland, right?

136
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:14,910
Master, don't you agree?

137
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,750
Working for the family

138
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,010
isn't hard work at all.

139
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:20,000
I test the waters in the Mainland,

140
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,920
and he holds the fort here.

141
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,240
We two brothers are working together

142
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:26,000
to grow the company.

143
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:29,210
Venturing out in the world

144
00:06:29,950 --> 00:06:31,410
can really toughen you up.

145
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,170
Look at Zhaohui now.

146
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:36,330
Zhaohui has become much more steady.

147
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,530
That's good.

148
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:39,090
I'm getting old.

149
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:40,830
Chengrong

150
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:43,350
will be handed over sooner or later.

151
00:06:48,630 --> 00:06:49,120
Daddy,

152
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:50,490
the company right now

153
00:06:50,490 --> 00:06:52,350
cannot do without you at the helm.

154
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,510
But you should

155
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,210
reduce your workload a bit.

156
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:57,190
I don't want you to get too tired.

157
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,510
I wish you a long life

158
00:06:58,630 --> 00:06:59,600
and good health.

159
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:00,830
Big Brother and I,

160
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:01,940
along with our younger siblings,

161
00:07:01,940 --> 00:07:02,800
still have so much

162
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,800
to learn from you.

163
00:07:07,310 --> 00:07:08,480
I won't let you down.

164
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:13,850
Do you know?

165
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:17,510
When I first came here,

166
00:07:19,310 --> 00:07:20,570
I started from scratch

167
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,180
with absolutely nothing.

168
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,920
I picked up

169
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:26,750
small fish and shrimp by the pier,

170
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,830
cured and boiled them,

171
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:29,690
then sold them.

172
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,800
Bit by bit, I earned my capital.

173
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,600
It took me 40 years

174
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,159
to build our Chengrong Group.

175
00:07:39,890 --> 00:07:40,970
I very much hope

176
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,270
that 40 years from now,

177
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:44,560
our Chengrong Group

178
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,330
will still be here.

179
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,750
I hope even more

180
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,800
that the person in charge

181
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,130
of Chengrong Group then

182
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,800
will still be a Du.

183
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,890
Of course,
it depends on everyone's ability.

184
00:08:00,980 --> 00:08:02,310
The most capable person

185
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:06,190
will succeed me, Du Chengrong.

186
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,780
Let's keep eating.

187
00:08:14,270 --> 00:08:14,830
Eat up.

188
00:08:14,930 --> 00:08:15,970
Carry on.

189
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:22,160
What was the old man

190
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,480
playing at just now?

191
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,420
He only said half of it,

192
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,810
acting all mysterious.

193
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:29,510
Young Master,

194
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:31,040
does your tooth still hurt?

195
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,360
I've already made an appointment

196
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,630
with Dr. Li.

197
00:08:34,789 --> 00:08:36,320
Tell him to wait for me at the hotel.

198
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,450
I'll go tell him now.

199
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:50,610
Are you seeing a doctor, Brother?

200
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,720
I heard you had an accident

201
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,580
in Shengcheng.

202
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:55,790
I wanted to go there to see you.

203
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:57,040
Why did you only plan

204
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,130
but not act on it?

205
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,080
Sorry, Brother.

206
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,790
The Group kept me too busy.

207
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:02,840
Forget it.

208
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,120
Save that act

209
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,480
to fool the old man.

210
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,820
Teach your mom while you're at it.

211
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:08,550
After dinner,

212
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:10,480
the old man ran off to his new flame.

213
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:11,990
You two are in danger.

214
00:09:13,370 --> 00:09:14,530
Don't assume that

215
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:16,440
just because you hold a seat,

216
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,370
you can call the shots in the Group.

217
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:23,760
Since we were young,

218
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,480
Daddy has always loved you the most.

219
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:28,330
I've always been envious.

220
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,450
I know you don't like me,

221
00:09:32,210 --> 00:09:33,120
thinking my mommy

222
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,450
destroyed your family.

223
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,240
But it's really difficult for us

224
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:39,240
to understand the elders' affairs.

225
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:40,120
If it weren't for my mommy,

226
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,550
it would have been someone else.

227
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:42,630
If you and I fight,

228
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:43,870
others in the family

229
00:09:43,870 --> 00:09:45,270
will only clap and cheer.

230
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:47,550
The Group is quite large.

231
00:09:48,510 --> 00:09:49,080
Brother,

232
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:50,750
why don't we join forces?

233
00:09:51,030 --> 00:09:52,290
With brothers united,

234
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:53,840
we can expand the Group.

235
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:58,960
As expected

236
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,890
of someone who has studied abroad!

237
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,640
You're so knowledgeable

238
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:04,270
and have a way with words.

239
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,480
In this regard,
you're a hundred times better than me.

240
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,340
Come on, drink.

241
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,570
Rest well, Brother.

242
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,270
I have other business at the company.

243
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:16,270
I'll be going now.

244
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,360
That Brat Ji.

245
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,340
Who does he take after?

246
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:27,560
The old man isn't like that either.

247
00:10:33,630 --> 00:10:34,480
Young Master.

248
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,960
In this big house,

249
00:10:38,550 --> 00:10:40,270
it is better to be cautious

250
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,600
with your words and actions.

251
00:10:43,790 --> 00:10:45,120
Do I need you to teach me?

252
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,620
Where is Liu Tianquan?

253
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,630
Tell him to come out.

254
00:10:48,630 --> 00:10:50,430
I have a score to settle with him.

255
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:52,540
For what happened in Shengcheng?

256
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:53,660
My brother told me.

257
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,860
The reason he wanted to win the bid

258
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:57,120
was just to help you out

259
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,200
in Shengcheng.

260
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:02,240
Do you think I'd believe you?

261
00:11:04,550 --> 00:11:06,720
It doesn't matter
if you believe it or not.

262
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,870
Having a project to work on

263
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:08,890
is better than letting the old man

264
00:11:08,890 --> 00:11:10,090
see this kind of news.

265
00:11:12,310 --> 00:11:13,640
[Chengrong's Eldest Young Master Fails to Woo Girl;
Love Turns to Hate as He Hits Someone with His Car]

266
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,810
Well? Isn't she pretty?

267
00:11:18,340 --> 00:11:19,320
The one that the old man

268
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,360
dances tango with—

269
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,150
what was her name?

270
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:21,840
Vivi?

271
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,000
Is she pretty?

272
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:24,360
She dances tango.

273
00:11:24,510 --> 00:11:25,570
Is she very pretty?

274
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,440
She dances tango.

275
00:11:28,290 --> 00:11:29,550
All I know is jump rope.

276
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:06,920
So beautiful.

277
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,150
This is what Zhaohui

278
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:16,600
takes from me the most.

279
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:17,910
Always go

280
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:20,360
for the prettiest girls.

281
00:12:22,660 --> 00:12:23,590
Don't you agree?

282
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,360
With me,

283
00:12:26,740 --> 00:12:28,910
you are not allowed to
mention other women.

284
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:29,840
I wouldn't dare.

285
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:42,720
It just so happens a colleague of mine

286
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,390
went on a business trip to Longcheng.

287
00:12:44,390 --> 00:12:44,790
Look,

288
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,800
doesn't it look convincing?

289
00:12:49,750 --> 00:12:50,510
Zhou Cheng,

290
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,220
this is the first time

291
00:12:52,220 --> 00:12:54,020
I've told such a big lie to my mom.

292
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:56,200
I'm actually a bit nervous.

293
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:57,440
What if she finds out?

294
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,550
It's a white lie.

295
00:12:59,670 --> 00:13:00,870
Your mother will understand.

296
00:13:00,870 --> 00:13:01,720
Besides,

297
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:04,130
she might not necessarily notice.

298
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:06,120
What was so urgent?

299
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,200
You didn't even have time

300
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,550
to come back and get your clothes.

301
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:09,390
Chen Xiliang suddenly

302
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:11,080
called me and said

303
00:13:11,100 --> 00:13:13,100
something happened at the factory.

304
00:13:13,150 --> 00:13:14,390
Like the sky was falling.

305
00:13:14,390 --> 00:13:15,670
So I didn't have time to pack,

306
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:16,670
and I just left.

307
00:13:17,390 --> 00:13:17,790
Right.

308
00:13:20,510 --> 00:13:21,710
What about your hand?

309
00:13:23,270 --> 00:13:24,800
What happened to your hand?

310
00:13:27,780 --> 00:13:29,980
I bumped into something at the factory.

311
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,670
I wrapped it up to prevent infection.

312
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,910
The doctor said
it'll be fine in a few days.

313
00:13:33,910 --> 00:13:35,000
I was quite worried too.

314
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,600
So as soon as I got back,

315
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,000
I took her to the hospital.

316
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,120
The doctor said she's fine.

317
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,180
I-I'm really fine.

318
00:13:39,390 --> 00:13:40,200
Fen.

319
00:13:40,730 --> 00:13:41,240
Granny Yu.

320
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,080
I'm thirsty.

321
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,540
Pour me some water.

322
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:52,480
Granny Yu,

323
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,510
thank you.

324
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:59,210
She's lying to her own mum so it's fine.

325
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:02,330
You're lying to your future mother-in-law.

326
00:14:02,330 --> 00:14:05,330
Aren't you afraid
she'll get back at you in the future?

327
00:14:05,510 --> 00:14:06,030
I...

328
00:14:06,130 --> 00:14:06,750
Granny Yu.

329
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:08,960
Do you want roast goose?

330
00:14:11,270 --> 00:14:13,070
From the shop at the intersection.

331
00:14:13,070 --> 00:14:14,070
With crispy skin.

332
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,000
-Okay.
-Okay.

333
00:14:16,670 --> 00:14:17,510
The one at the intersection.

334
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:18,720
The skin has to be crispy.
Did you hear that?

335
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:19,390
I heard that.

336
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:19,990
You buy it.

337
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:20,860
I'll buy it.

338
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,720
Do you think

339
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,780
Granny Yu will like this roast goose?

340
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:25,810
How could she not?

341
00:14:25,810 --> 00:14:27,200
Isn't roast goose her favorite?

342
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:27,670
Is it?

343
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:30,130
She'll definitely like it.

344
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:35,960
I'm sorry.

345
00:14:36,170 --> 00:14:37,500
I really didn't mean to.

346
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:45,250
It's okay. Go ahead.

347
00:14:45,570 --> 00:14:46,200
Thank you, Miss.

348
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,060
Goodbye, Miss.

349
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:47,650
Goodbye.

350
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,340
Do you know her?

351
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,320
No.

352
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,720
I just envy her.

353
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:02,630
To be able to, in her best years,

354
00:15:02,790 --> 00:15:03,630
be carefree

355
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:04,970
and laugh so freely.

356
00:15:07,150 --> 00:15:08,000
How do you know

357
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:09,430
these are her best years?

358
00:15:10,210 --> 00:15:11,520
Maybe when she was 6,

359
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:12,960
she was even more carefree.

360
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,240
Or at 26,

361
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:15,690
she might be even freer.

362
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:17,240
You mean

363
00:15:17,610 --> 00:15:18,910
I'll have my best years too,

364
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:19,440
right?

365
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:21,720
I mean

366
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,000
life is long—

367
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,240
who knows

368
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,440
when the best time is?

369
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:27,630
To enjoy this moment,

370
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:28,810
do your best,

371
00:15:29,030 --> 00:15:30,160
and leave no regrets

372
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:32,140
would make it your best years.

373
00:15:32,870 --> 00:15:33,530
Zhou Cheng,

374
00:15:34,390 --> 00:15:35,850
are you enjoying yourself

375
00:15:35,870 --> 00:15:36,800
and happy enough

376
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:37,730
at this moment?

377
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:41,150
If I could be your family,

378
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:43,090
that would be even better.

379
00:15:46,870 --> 00:15:48,130
With this roast goose,

380
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,680
we'd be able to clear

381
00:15:49,870 --> 00:15:50,960
Granny Yu.

382
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:53,840
By the way,

383
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:55,270
I might need to go

384
00:15:55,270 --> 00:15:56,670
to Xiangcheng tomorrow.

385
00:15:56,870 --> 00:15:58,130
Will you be okay alone?

386
00:15:59,200 --> 00:15:59,720
Me?

387
00:16:00,880 --> 00:16:01,820
The guesthouse bid's results

388
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:03,150
are out tomorrow, right?

389
00:16:03,150 --> 00:16:04,480
Did I remember wrongly?

390
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:05,390
No, no.

391
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:06,920
I just almost forgot.

392
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:07,930
Don't worry.

393
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:10,030
Second Uncle warned Du Zhaohui,

394
00:16:10,030 --> 00:16:11,790
and Du Zhaohui warned Liu Tianquan.

395
00:16:11,790 --> 00:16:12,270
I doubt they

396
00:16:12,270 --> 00:16:13,720
would dare to do anything.

397
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,910
Let's go. Hurry inside.

398
00:16:14,910 --> 00:16:15,750
If we don't go in now,

399
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:18,280
the roast goose skin
won't be crispy anymore.

400
00:16:20,090 --> 00:16:24,730
[Shengcheng Guesthouse Renovation Auction]

401
00:16:21,390 --> 00:16:23,450
So, that's settled for this project.

402
00:16:23,480 --> 00:16:25,610
Does anyone have any other questions?

403
00:16:25,910 --> 00:16:27,360
I'd like to ask—

404
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:29,200
do you have something against

405
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,330
Gangdao merchants?

406
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:32,720
Since the project can be subcontracted,

407
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:34,200
why are we the only ones

408
00:16:34,510 --> 00:16:35,520
being excluded?

409
00:16:36,390 --> 00:16:37,080
Comrade,

410
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,970
we invited experts to vote.

411
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:40,250
During the vote,

412
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:41,320
we didn't disclose

413
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:43,270
the bidding entity for each proposal.

414
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:44,670
There couldn't be any bias.

415
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:46,730
It was purely based on the proposals.

416
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,810
Based on the proposals?

417
00:16:49,390 --> 00:16:50,240
With that

418
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:52,000
tiny little company of theirs?

419
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:53,120
They've only done

420
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:54,600
interior decoration before.

421
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:55,320
How could their proposal

422
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:57,180
be better than ours at Chengrong?

423
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:00,960
The proposal doesn't just need to be good;

424
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,550
it also needs to be suitable.

425
00:17:02,550 --> 00:17:03,630
Chengrong Tianchen's proposal

426
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:04,640
is too luxurious

427
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:05,640
for us.

428
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:07,609
As for Yuanhui,

429
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,040
they provided

430
00:17:09,310 --> 00:17:11,240
the most suitable proposal for us.

431
00:17:11,550 --> 00:17:13,680
Although they are only renovating
two dining halls,

432
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:15,410
but for the entire guesthouse,

433
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,230
we also plan

434
00:17:16,829 --> 00:17:18,089
to use their proposal.

435
00:17:18,109 --> 00:17:19,109
What does that mean?

436
00:17:19,109 --> 00:17:21,240
We Shengyijian won the guest room bid,

437
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:21,880
but we have to execute

438
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:23,280
according to their plan?

439
00:17:23,349 --> 00:17:24,400
That's not appropriate, is it?

440
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:24,829
Right.

441
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:27,170
Comrade Xia,

442
00:17:27,550 --> 00:17:29,310
can you show your drawings

443
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:31,100
to these gentlemen right now?

444
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:32,460
Of course, no problem.

445
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:33,720
I'd be happy to let this gentleman

446
00:17:33,720 --> 00:17:34,790
who didn't win the bid

447
00:17:34,790 --> 00:17:36,790
accept his defeat wholeheartedly.

448
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:37,830
Uncle.

449
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,110
Here.

450
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:44,340
Thanks.

451
00:17:45,110 --> 00:17:45,770
Here you go.

452
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:46,900
Take a look.

453
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,590
Look at this design.

454
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:52,330
It's indeed quite good.

455
00:17:54,310 --> 00:17:55,160
Take a look at this one too.

456
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:56,000
Haven't seen these before.

457
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:56,400
Right.

458
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,460
Since that's the case,

459
00:17:58,640 --> 00:17:59,830
let them handle it.

460
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:02,350
But regarding the details,

461
00:18:02,350 --> 00:18:03,000
we still need to

462
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:03,810
communicate with Yuanhui's designers

463
00:18:03,810 --> 00:18:04,570
further.

464
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:05,270
Okay.

465
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:07,120
This proposal is not bad.

466
00:18:07,550 --> 00:18:08,450
This design

467
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:09,480
is very original.

468
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:10,010
Look.

469
00:18:10,070 --> 00:18:11,480
I've never seen anything like it.

470
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:13,160
It brings out the full effect.

471
00:18:16,270 --> 00:18:17,550
This is a design drawing?

472
00:18:17,550 --> 00:18:18,030
Yes.

473
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:20,530
You haven't seen one before, have you?

474
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:39,200
Ms. Xia.

475
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:40,700
Congratulations.

476
00:18:41,040 --> 00:18:42,240
I heard this is Yuanhui's first ever bid

477
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:44,070
and you won it.

478
00:18:44,590 --> 00:18:45,790
That calls for a celebration.

479
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:46,480
Mr. Du,

480
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:49,020
although Yuanhui is a small company,

481
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:50,130
I'm confident

482
00:18:50,160 --> 00:18:51,560
it's as good as any other.

483
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,960
Chengrong might dominate Gangdao,

484
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:55,590
but it might not suit the mainland.

485
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:56,480
In this bid,

486
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:58,280
Chengrong was pretty lousy.

487
00:18:58,750 --> 00:19:01,080
But because of your interference, Mr. Du,

488
00:19:01,370 --> 00:19:02,520
it made Mr. Liu

489
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:04,420
think they went easy on us.

490
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:06,240
Xia Xiaolan.

491
00:19:06,550 --> 00:19:07,640
That's enough.

492
00:19:09,150 --> 00:19:11,210
Ms. Xia is still as straightforward.

493
00:19:11,270 --> 00:19:11,930
I like that.

494
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,790
But I came here today

495
00:19:13,790 --> 00:19:14,920
for something else.

496
00:19:15,730 --> 00:19:17,410
The lawyers have settled

497
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:18,720
Kang Wei's compensation.

498
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:21,200
As for Mr. Liu's car,

499
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:23,560
I've made an appointment
with the dealership.

500
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:24,830
Are you interested in coming with me

501
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:26,030
to take a look?

502
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:28,180
The car is being compensated to me.

503
00:19:28,180 --> 00:19:29,400
Why would Xiaolan go?

504
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:31,030
If Mr. Liu wants to go,

505
00:19:31,030 --> 00:19:31,980
you can come along too.

506
00:19:31,980 --> 00:19:32,450
No need.

507
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:33,830
Just replace it with the same model.

508
00:19:33,830 --> 00:19:35,360
That car was already so old.

509
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:36,680
Wait a moment, wait.

510
00:19:39,350 --> 00:19:40,750
Why not choose a new one?

511
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:42,970
Let's go.

512
00:19:43,280 --> 00:19:44,240
I'll buy you a different model.

513
00:19:44,240 --> 00:19:44,900
How's that?

514
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:54,920
Don't be so polite with me.

515
00:19:55,860 --> 00:19:57,010
Sis Bai, I've caused you trouble

516
00:19:57,010 --> 00:19:58,210
these few days.

517
00:19:58,780 --> 00:20:00,120
Let's go get some Japanese food.

518
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:00,830
Cheng took me

519
00:20:00,830 --> 00:20:02,030
to eat it in Jingcheng before.

520
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:03,160
I heard one opened in Shengcheng too.

521
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:04,020
Let's go try it.

522
00:20:04,110 --> 00:20:05,480
You're still thinking about eating?

523
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,310
My shop hasn't been properly managed

524
00:20:06,310 --> 00:20:07,510
these few days.

525
00:20:07,840 --> 00:20:09,700
Still thinking about eating out?

526
00:20:09,790 --> 00:20:11,000
You are right.

527
00:20:11,030 --> 00:20:12,360
Let's make money first.

528
00:20:12,590 --> 00:20:14,250
We'll eat after we make money.

529
00:20:15,750 --> 00:20:16,750
Which arm did you injure?

530
00:20:16,750 --> 00:20:17,280
This one.

531
00:20:18,450 --> 00:20:18,960
Don't, don't!

532
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:20,560
It just healed, just healed.

533
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:22,680
Mom.

534
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:23,520
Mrs. Kang.

535
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:25,400
Where is Second Uncle?

536
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:27,400
He went to the entrance to hail a cab.

537
00:20:27,510 --> 00:20:28,440
Ms. Zhenzhu.

538
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:30,510
Let's have dinner together tonight.

539
00:20:30,510 --> 00:20:31,750
No need to trouble yourselves—

540
00:20:31,750 --> 00:20:32,400
Sis Bai.

541
00:20:33,070 --> 00:20:35,240
I've just survived a disaster.

542
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:36,310
You have to go

543
00:20:36,330 --> 00:20:36,830
to join in

544
00:20:36,830 --> 00:20:37,440
the fun

545
00:20:37,510 --> 00:20:38,090
and wash away the bad luck.

546
00:20:38,090 --> 00:20:39,220
Invite Xiaolan too.

547
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:40,500
Let's all go together.

548
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:42,000
Then I'll trouble you, Ma'am.

549
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:42,570
Hurry, hurry.

550
00:20:42,570 --> 00:20:43,750
-Let's go.
-Not at all.

551
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:44,840
Let's eat. Let's eat.

552
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:45,590
I'll carry it. I'll carry it.

553
00:20:45,590 --> 00:20:46,200
Let's go.

554
00:20:46,220 --> 00:20:46,950
I'll take it!

555
00:20:47,750 --> 00:20:48,160
Hey—

556
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:49,610
You've got them all?

557
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:04,480
Second Uncle.

558
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:05,680
Let's go eat.

559
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:06,750
Don't make Sis Bai

560
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:07,610
and my mom wait.

561
00:21:09,510 --> 00:21:09,960
Come.

562
00:21:10,590 --> 00:21:11,850
Pull up a stool and sit.

563
00:21:12,030 --> 00:21:12,690
Let's chat.

564
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:14,070
Second Uncle.

565
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:16,170
Sit down.

566
00:21:26,180 --> 00:21:26,960
Sit, Zhenzhu, sit.

567
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:27,400
Okay.

568
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,110
Have some tea.

569
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:31,240
Okay, thanks.

570
00:21:33,990 --> 00:21:34,520
Zhenzhu.

571
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:35,880
I'll do it. I'll do it.

572
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:37,030
Your arm just healed.

573
00:21:37,030 --> 00:21:38,030
I'll do it myself.

574
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:39,240
Thank you.

575
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:43,270
Are you a Shengcheng local?

576
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:45,200
I'm from Longcheng.

577
00:21:46,830 --> 00:21:48,750
My family
used to run a martial arts school.

578
00:21:48,750 --> 00:21:49,790
After the school closed down,

579
00:21:49,790 --> 00:21:51,310
I came out to do business.

580
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:52,970
Xiaolan told me

581
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:53,880
that there'd be more opportunities

582
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:55,010
here in Shengcheng,

583
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:56,310
so I came here.

584
00:21:58,350 --> 00:21:59,920
So, is your family all here?

585
00:22:01,890 --> 00:22:03,210
It's just my grandma

586
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:04,440
and me now.

587
00:22:04,790 --> 00:22:05,860
Grandma is old,

588
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:07,520
so I have to bring her with me.

589
00:22:09,170 --> 00:22:10,810
You've had it tough, girl.

590
00:22:12,790 --> 00:22:14,190
What is your zodiac sign?

591
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:16,510
I heard Wei call you Sis Bai.

592
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:17,940
Are you older than him?

593
00:22:20,120 --> 00:22:21,890
I'm the same age as Wei.

594
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:23,590
He probably calls me Sis

595
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,530
because I'm a good fighter?

596
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,680
He calls Xiaolan Sis too,

597
00:22:27,930 --> 00:22:28,830
even though Xiaolan is actually

598
00:22:28,830 --> 00:22:30,160
a year younger than him.

599
00:22:39,350 --> 00:22:40,150
Have some tea.

600
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:41,620
Please, have some tea too.

601
00:22:44,030 --> 00:22:45,160
I'll go check why Xiaolan

602
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,070
isn't here yet.

603
00:22:47,110 --> 00:22:48,000
Slow down.

604
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:51,200
Look at this kid.

605
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,590
She's shy.

606
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:54,800
Second Uncle,

607
00:22:55,160 --> 00:22:55,980
doing business

608
00:22:55,980 --> 00:22:57,130
isn't that easy.

609
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,290
Since it's not easy,

610
00:22:58,350 --> 00:22:59,680
go back to your job.

611
00:23:00,270 --> 00:23:01,130
I won't go back.

612
00:23:01,730 --> 00:23:02,450
If I go back,

613
00:23:02,480 --> 00:23:03,110
for the rest of my life,

614
00:23:03,110 --> 00:23:04,270
I'll have to listen to you.

615
00:23:04,270 --> 00:23:04,880
Whatever you say,

616
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:05,880
I'll have to do it.

617
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:06,550
Whatever we say

618
00:23:06,550 --> 00:23:07,750
is for your own good.

619
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:09,160
Would we harm you?

620
00:23:09,640 --> 00:23:11,750
I know you wouldn't harm me.

621
00:23:12,030 --> 00:23:12,790
But you would turn me

622
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:13,960
into a loser.

623
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:16,090
What are you saying?

624
00:23:16,590 --> 00:23:17,310
Second Uncle,

625
00:23:17,310 --> 00:23:19,110
I used to think you didn't train me

626
00:23:19,110 --> 00:23:20,000
or value me.

627
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,510
But while I was in the hospital,

628
00:23:21,510 --> 00:23:23,380
I realized you really care about me.

629
00:23:23,380 --> 00:23:24,750
Maybe you feel bad

630
00:23:24,830 --> 00:23:26,270
that I lost my dad when I was young,

631
00:23:26,270 --> 00:23:28,070
so you didn't want to be harsh on me.

632
00:23:28,070 --> 00:23:29,110
You wanted me to have an easy

633
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:30,370
and comfortable life.

634
00:23:30,750 --> 00:23:32,030
But no one has it easy.

635
00:23:32,310 --> 00:23:33,170
Look at Sis Bai.

636
00:23:33,310 --> 00:23:34,830
When she first came to Longcheng,

637
00:23:34,830 --> 00:23:36,360
she was just a fruit seller.

638
00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:38,550
She worked for 5 years
before she could open a shop.

639
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:39,520
Xiaolan, too.

640
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:41,340
She used to sell duck eggs in Anqing.

641
00:23:41,340 --> 00:23:43,250
She made it here dime by dime.

642
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:44,510
Cheng.

643
00:23:44,750 --> 00:23:46,550
He's a top student from Huaqing,

644
00:23:46,590 --> 00:23:48,210
but he started out
by doing odd jobs at a law firm.

645
00:23:48,210 --> 00:23:49,110
None of them had it easy.

646
00:23:49,110 --> 00:23:50,440
But they didn't give up.

647
00:23:50,590 --> 00:23:52,240
Can you compare yourself to them?

648
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,760
They have drive and grit.

649
00:23:53,790 --> 00:23:55,050
Do you have the brains?

650
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:56,480
Do you?

651
00:23:57,750 --> 00:23:58,440
Talk!

652
00:23:59,550 --> 00:24:00,160
Yes.

653
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:01,110
I don't.

654
00:24:01,360 --> 00:24:02,250
I'm not as smart

655
00:24:02,550 --> 00:24:04,010
or as hardworking as them.

656
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:08,480
But...

657
00:24:08,670 --> 00:24:09,930
But I can change.

658
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:11,110
I can learn.

659
00:24:11,550 --> 00:24:12,510
In the past, you guys

660
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:13,710
always protected me.

661
00:24:13,750 --> 00:24:14,680
Now I just want

662
00:24:14,790 --> 00:24:16,120
to venture out on my own.

663
00:24:16,270 --> 00:24:17,670
It is harder than before,

664
00:24:17,750 --> 00:24:19,160
but I'm happier too.

665
00:24:19,270 --> 00:24:20,310
Even if I earn 10 yuan,

666
00:24:20,310 --> 00:24:21,550
I can be happy all day.

667
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:24,440
Anyway, I don't care.

668
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:25,790
I'm staying in Shengcheng.

669
00:24:25,790 --> 00:24:26,990
I won't be a deserter.

670
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:39,790
Hello, Mrs. Kang.

671
00:24:39,790 --> 00:24:41,050
You're here, Xiaolan.

672
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:41,750
Zhenzhu.

673
00:24:41,750 --> 00:24:42,610
Come, sit here.

674
00:24:42,880 --> 00:24:43,440
I...

675
00:24:43,590 --> 00:24:44,000
Come on.

676
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:44,800
Sit down. Sit.

677
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:45,640
Sit.

678
00:24:46,030 --> 00:24:46,440
Okay.

679
00:24:49,550 --> 00:24:50,150
Mrs. Kang,

680
00:24:50,790 --> 00:24:52,790
Zhenzhu has something to say to you.

681
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,590
It's about her and Wei.

682
00:24:56,510 --> 00:24:57,070
Go ahead.

683
00:24:58,350 --> 00:24:58,950
Mrs. Kang,

684
00:24:59,420 --> 00:25:00,880
although I don't really understand

685
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:02,140
these kinds of things,

686
00:25:02,270 --> 00:25:02,880
I think

687
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:04,540
you must have misunderstood.

688
00:25:04,550 --> 00:25:05,550
Wei and I

689
00:25:05,750 --> 00:25:07,000
are friends.

690
00:25:07,830 --> 00:25:09,720
We are business partners.

691
00:25:10,310 --> 00:25:11,790
We have a good relationship, but...

692
00:25:11,790 --> 00:25:12,240
it's not

693
00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:13,510
what you think.

694
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:21,270
Sorry!

695
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:28,960
You child...

696
00:25:29,790 --> 00:25:31,030
You are quite direct.

697
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:33,350
Okay.

698
00:25:34,030 --> 00:25:35,720
Since you've put it that way,

699
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:38,000
I understand now.

700
00:25:39,070 --> 00:25:40,070
Come on, sit down.

701
00:25:40,350 --> 00:25:41,200
Mom.

702
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,810
What do you know now?

703
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:45,830
I know that you are still

704
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:47,000
a disappointment.

705
00:25:50,650 --> 00:25:51,350
-Hello, Mr. Kang.
-Hello, Mr. Kang.

706
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:51,750
Hello.

707
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:52,410
Sit, sit.

708
00:25:55,830 --> 00:25:56,200
Sit.

709
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:00,510
Come.

710
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:04,710
This first glass of wine,

711
00:26:05,070 --> 00:26:06,830
I'd like to toast
to all our young friends here

712
00:26:06,830 --> 00:26:08,100
for taking care of

713
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,840
Kang Wei these past few days.

714
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:10,590
Come.

715
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,220
This second glass,

716
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:18,590
I'd like to toast
to Ms. Bai Zhenzhu.

717
00:26:20,440 --> 00:26:22,480
Thank you for kicking Du Zhaohui.

718
00:26:24,030 --> 00:26:25,230
No need to be nervous.

719
00:26:25,970 --> 00:26:27,110
You did what everyone wanted to do

720
00:26:27,110 --> 00:26:28,110
but was afraid to.

721
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:30,310
Thank you
for treating Kang Wei as a friend

722
00:26:30,310 --> 00:26:31,640
and standing up for him.

723
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:33,350
It was impulsive,

724
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:36,310
but also it was also
out of loyalty and righteousness.

725
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:37,110
Rest assured.

726
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:39,000
If the Du family

727
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:40,570
gives you any trouble,

728
00:26:41,110 --> 00:26:43,370
the Kang family
will take full responsibility.

729
00:26:43,370 --> 00:26:44,570
This glass is for you.

730
00:26:44,790 --> 00:26:47,050
Sorry for causing you trouble, Mr. Kang.

731
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:48,400
Sit.

732
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:51,750
Don't be nervous.

733
00:26:52,160 --> 00:26:54,220
I'm just Kang Wei's parent right now.

734
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:56,200
It's only right that I thank you.

735
00:26:56,680 --> 00:26:58,210
As for whether you should be

736
00:26:58,550 --> 00:26:59,880
that impulsive in the future,

737
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:01,790
and how to control your impulses,

738
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:03,240
you should really

739
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:04,300
learn a thing or two

740
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:05,640
from your good friend here,

741
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:06,880
Xia Xiaolan.

742
00:27:07,070 --> 00:27:08,200
Thank you, Mr. Kang.

743
00:27:09,120 --> 00:27:10,680
Whether Kang Wei makes money in the south

744
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:11,480
is secondary.

745
00:27:12,240 --> 00:27:13,440
The most important thing is that

746
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:15,570
he has made such good friends like you.

747
00:27:17,550 --> 00:27:19,480
Your trip to Shengcheng this time,

748
00:27:19,590 --> 00:27:20,200
Kang Wei,

749
00:27:20,750 --> 00:27:21,810
was worth the trip.

750
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:24,520
Second Uncle.

751
00:27:24,800 --> 00:27:26,530
You're agreeing to let me stay?

752
00:27:31,590 --> 00:27:32,050
Come on.

753
00:27:32,430 --> 00:27:33,160
Let's eat.

754
00:27:35,300 --> 00:27:36,700
Second Uncle, you first.

755
00:27:39,410 --> 00:27:40,860
Second Uncle, eat up.

756
00:27:43,010 --> 00:27:46,640
[Winter, 1989]

757
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:55,440
Hello!

758
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:57,370
As you asked,

759
00:27:57,550 --> 00:27:58,680
I got you a new one.

760
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,460
The paperwork is all done.

761
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,310
Ms. Xia.

762
00:28:01,590 --> 00:28:03,400
Your car is too ugly.

763
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:04,780
Why don't I buy a new

764
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:06,080
and nicer one for you?

765
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:07,070
My uncle

766
00:28:07,070 --> 00:28:08,590
is supervising work
at Shengcheng Guesthouse.

767
00:28:08,590 --> 00:28:09,650
Send it over there.

768
00:28:10,550 --> 00:28:11,680
Drive it to Shengcheng Guesthouse.

769
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:12,070
Go on.

770
00:28:12,510 --> 00:28:13,310
Where are you going?

771
00:28:13,310 --> 00:28:14,070
I'll give you a ride.

772
00:28:14,070 --> 00:28:14,590
It's faster.

773
00:28:14,590 --> 00:28:15,790
Get in my car. Come on.

774
00:28:16,790 --> 00:28:17,440
What are you doing?

775
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:17,960
What are you doing?

776
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:18,620
Who are you?

777
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:19,400
What's your problem?

778
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:20,070
Let go!

779
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:26,320
Xiaolan.

780
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:27,580
This is Ge Jian.

781
00:28:27,720 --> 00:28:29,590
He was also a disciple
at Bai Martial Arts School.

782
00:28:29,590 --> 00:28:30,270
When you go out,

783
00:28:30,270 --> 00:28:31,790
you need a driver and a bodyguard.

784
00:28:31,790 --> 00:28:32,350
Since I'm going on
a business trip this time,

785
00:28:32,350 --> 00:28:33,410
I brought him over.

786
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:34,930
How thoughtful.

787
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:36,160
Ge Jian.

788
00:28:36,590 --> 00:28:38,440
Today is your first day.

789
00:28:38,630 --> 00:28:39,760
Your first job is

790
00:28:39,790 --> 00:28:41,240
to make this man in purple

791
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:42,240
stay away from me.

792
00:28:42,360 --> 00:28:43,030
And him too.

793
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:44,960
Okay, Ms. Xia.

794
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:45,840
Let's go.

795
00:28:46,330 --> 00:28:47,930
Where are you going, Ms. Xia?

796
00:28:48,590 --> 00:28:49,450
Ge Jian, right?

797
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:50,700
I'll remember you!

798
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:51,880
Get in.

799
00:28:51,880 --> 00:28:52,400
Ge Jian!

800
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:54,280
I'll remember you too, Ge Jian!

801
00:28:55,070 --> 00:28:56,890
Come to Gangdao if you have the guts.

802
00:28:56,890 --> 00:28:57,830
Think you're tough because you're big?

803
00:28:57,830 --> 00:28:59,360
It's just useless muscles.

804
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,320
Here. Careful, it's hot.

805
00:29:06,960 --> 00:29:07,920
Second Uncle agreed

806
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:09,110
to let Kang Wei stay

807
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,170
because he wants to push us.

808
00:29:11,510 --> 00:29:12,640
Although each of us

809
00:29:12,640 --> 00:29:13,830
has a business to run,

810
00:29:13,830 --> 00:29:15,160
none of them are on a large scale.

811
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:16,900
There are opportunities
everywhere in Shengcheng,

812
00:29:16,900 --> 00:29:18,490
but few have made it big.

813
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:20,480
Xiaolan.

814
00:29:21,030 --> 00:29:21,590
Since you say that,

815
00:29:21,590 --> 00:29:22,650
do you have an idea?

816
00:29:23,240 --> 00:29:24,790
Uncle has now secured

817
00:29:25,070 --> 00:29:26,840
the renovation
of the guesthouse restaurant.

818
00:29:26,840 --> 00:29:27,590
As for building materials,

819
00:29:27,590 --> 00:29:29,070
we can get them from Zhenzhu.

820
00:29:29,070 --> 00:29:30,440
The projects we handle in the future

821
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:31,640
will only get bigger.

822
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:32,510
The shop right now

823
00:29:32,510 --> 00:29:33,510
isn't big enough?

824
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:34,480
It's small.

825
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:35,770
And anyone can do it.

826
00:29:35,790 --> 00:29:37,050
There's no advantage.

827
00:29:37,550 --> 00:29:38,350
I think

828
00:29:38,590 --> 00:29:40,650
we can build a building materials center.

829
00:29:40,650 --> 00:29:42,110
In the future,
whether it's residential housing

830
00:29:42,110 --> 00:29:43,270
or commercial renovation,

831
00:29:43,270 --> 00:29:44,350
whenever someone mentions
building materials,

832
00:29:44,350 --> 00:29:45,110
the first thing they'll think of

833
00:29:45,110 --> 00:29:45,790
is us.

834
00:29:45,830 --> 00:29:47,630
As Shengcheng develops faster,

835
00:29:47,790 --> 00:29:49,720
where there's a market, there's demand.

836
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:50,920
Instead of waiting for others

837
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:51,640
to take this business,

838
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,160
we should

839
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:54,000
seize the opportunity ourselves.

840
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:54,440
Okay.

841
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:56,750
I'll discuss it with Sis Bai

842
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:58,140
and come up with a plan.

843
00:29:58,730 --> 00:30:00,070
You know how to make plans now,

844
00:30:00,070 --> 00:30:00,640
Wei?

845
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:02,200
You're amazing.

846
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,060
Zhou Cheng.

847
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:11,940
Did you try the meatballs?

848
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,040
Yes, I did.

849
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:15,440
It's the best time for

850
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:17,100
mutton hotpot when it's cold.

851
00:30:17,210 --> 00:30:18,000
But I feel like

852
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,070
the mutton here

853
00:30:19,130 --> 00:30:19,790
isn't as authentic as

854
00:30:19,790 --> 00:30:21,510
what we had in the capital.

855
00:30:22,750 --> 00:30:23,880
By the way, Cheng Zi,

856
00:30:23,880 --> 00:30:26,000
your trip to Jingcheng this time...

857
00:30:32,670 --> 00:30:34,200
You went back to Jingcheng?

858
00:30:42,030 --> 00:30:42,590
Xiaolan.

859
00:30:43,720 --> 00:30:45,920
It was a sudden trip,

860
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:47,310
so I didn't tell you.

861
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:49,240
I'm sorry.

862
00:30:50,070 --> 00:30:50,680
It's fine.

863
00:30:51,270 --> 00:30:52,400
We're all busy.

864
00:30:52,730 --> 00:30:54,070
Forgetting things occasionally

865
00:30:54,070 --> 00:30:54,680
is normal.

866
00:30:57,270 --> 00:30:58,920
How is work lately?

867
00:30:59,070 --> 00:31:00,000
Is it going well?

868
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:01,330
It's going well.

869
00:31:01,790 --> 00:31:03,450
I've started handling cases.

870
00:31:03,830 --> 00:31:05,030
It's quite fulfilling.

871
00:31:05,030 --> 00:31:07,160
It's just that some things are tricky,

872
00:31:07,200 --> 00:31:08,930
and haven't been resolved yet.

873
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:12,800
What's wrong?

874
00:31:13,550 --> 00:31:14,240
Nothing.

875
00:31:14,480 --> 00:31:15,810
It's almost New Year's.

876
00:31:16,510 --> 00:31:17,030
Yeah.

877
00:31:17,790 --> 00:31:19,120
It's almost New Year's.

878
00:31:28,030 --> 00:31:29,230
I'm heading back now.

879
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:30,450
Bye-bye.

880
00:31:30,590 --> 00:31:31,120
Bye-bye.

881
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:08,920
Wei,

882
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,250
you really act fast now.

883
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:12,010
You're planning already?

884
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:14,280
I was all geared up to plan,

885
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:16,370
then got discouraged and shelved it.

886
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:18,740
What happened?

887
00:32:18,750 --> 00:32:19,270
Look.

888
00:32:20,400 --> 00:32:21,930
Sis Bai and I calculated it.

889
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:23,350
For a shop,

890
00:32:23,530 --> 00:32:25,130
the renovation and rent

891
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:26,320
aren't the biggest expenses.

892
00:32:26,320 --> 00:32:27,240
The main thing is,

893
00:32:27,240 --> 00:32:29,160
for the scale Xiaolan mentioned,

894
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:30,890
it requires a lot of

895
00:32:30,910 --> 00:32:32,370
upfront inventory costs;

896
00:32:32,640 --> 00:32:34,200
only then can you stock the shop

897
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:34,800
properly.

898
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:36,920
A rough estimate shows

899
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:39,180
we need at least 300,000 yuan in capital.

900
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:40,590
Cheng,

901
00:32:41,250 --> 00:32:43,180
how much is your salary this month?

902
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:45,110
It's about 300.

903
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,680
Do you know

904
00:32:47,770 --> 00:32:48,790
how much profit

905
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:50,480
Sis Bai and my stall make now?

906
00:32:51,270 --> 00:32:52,240
Less than 3,000.

907
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:53,000
Tell me,

908
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:55,130
how long will it take to get enough?

909
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:56,440
3,000?

910
00:32:58,350 --> 00:32:59,750
Self-employed people really make more.

911
00:32:59,750 --> 00:33:00,590
But those profits

912
00:33:00,590 --> 00:33:02,000
don't go into our pockets.

913
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:02,920
They are all reinvested

914
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:04,250
to expand the business.

915
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:07,750
The goal is ambitious,

916
00:33:08,030 --> 00:33:09,880
but the path is winding.

917
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:11,110
Right now,

918
00:33:11,440 --> 00:33:12,830
I just need to work hard,

919
00:33:13,160 --> 00:33:14,160
fight hard,

920
00:33:14,310 --> 00:33:15,970
and make something of myself!

921
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:17,950
All right.

922
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,420
Then go make something of yourself

923
00:33:19,420 --> 00:33:20,110
and show me.

924
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:21,550
You bet!

925
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:26,920
Chen, this isn't like you.

926
00:33:27,110 --> 00:33:28,710
Have you asked the magazine?

927
00:33:29,120 --> 00:33:30,310
If you have any problems using it,

928
00:33:30,310 --> 00:33:31,240
feel free to contact me anytime.

929
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,170
Okay, thank you.

930
00:33:32,270 --> 00:33:33,130
Appreciate it.

931
00:33:33,510 --> 00:33:34,910
How about the TV station?

932
00:33:36,790 --> 00:33:37,440
Granny Yu.

933
00:33:38,110 --> 00:33:39,720
The phone was just installed,

934
00:33:39,720 --> 00:33:41,850
and she's already doing business calls?

935
00:33:41,850 --> 00:33:42,720
Xiaolan said

936
00:33:42,750 --> 00:33:44,020
she has to earn back the installation fee

937
00:33:44,020 --> 00:33:45,230
as soon as possible.

938
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:45,960
Really?

939
00:33:46,000 --> 00:33:46,800
Impressive.

940
00:33:47,880 --> 00:33:48,480
Granny Yu.

941
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:50,270
I made

942
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:51,890
fig and spare rib soup.

943
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:53,030
Could you go check on it for me?

944
00:33:53,030 --> 00:33:53,480
Okay.

945
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:55,040
I'll go check.

946
00:33:57,960 --> 00:33:58,400
No,

947
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:00,920
you can't just give up like this.

948
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:02,110
If this works,

949
00:34:02,310 --> 00:34:03,400
Luna will succeed.

950
00:34:04,030 --> 00:34:04,590
Xiaolan,

951
00:34:04,920 --> 00:34:06,590
I've gone through all the friends

952
00:34:06,590 --> 00:34:07,400
and connections

953
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:08,510
that I can find.

954
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:10,969
I really don't have any contacts
for the Chinese New Year Gala.

955
00:34:10,969 --> 00:34:11,960
If you don't have connections,

956
00:34:11,960 --> 00:34:13,510
then create them.

957
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:15,510
If we can't get into
their costume department,

958
00:34:15,510 --> 00:34:17,150
there are other departments too.

959
00:34:17,150 --> 00:34:18,000
If all else fails,

960
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:19,710
they must need people
to help hand out box lunches, right?

961
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:20,900
As long as you can get in,

962
00:34:20,900 --> 00:34:22,320
you'll meet more people.

963
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:24,190
With your smarts,

964
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:25,960
it won't be hard to find a way.

965
00:34:26,190 --> 00:34:27,320
Don't worry.

966
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:28,739
I'm asking around too.

967
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:30,880
We're fighting side by side now.

968
00:34:31,070 --> 00:34:32,969
I'll let you know as soon as I have news.

969
00:34:32,969 --> 00:34:33,760
I believe

970
00:34:33,850 --> 00:34:34,920
that until the very last moment,

971
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:35,960
you won't give up.

972
00:34:36,070 --> 00:34:36,510
Right?

973
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:39,199
Since you put it that way,

974
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:40,230
all right,

975
00:34:40,590 --> 00:34:41,449
I won't give up.

976
00:34:42,230 --> 00:34:43,510
I've bought the plane ticket.

977
00:34:43,510 --> 00:34:44,920
I'll arrive in Jingcheng tonight.

978
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:45,320
Okay.

979
00:34:45,630 --> 00:34:47,360
You'll surely be busy on New Year's Eve.

980
00:34:47,360 --> 00:34:48,510
So I'll wish you

981
00:34:48,550 --> 00:34:49,710
a Happy New Year in advance.

982
00:34:49,710 --> 00:34:50,570
Happy New Year.

983
00:34:51,000 --> 00:34:51,600
Good luck.

984
00:35:06,670 --> 00:35:08,030
My goodness.

985
00:35:08,770 --> 00:35:10,110
We're going back for the New Year,

986
00:35:10,110 --> 00:35:10,840
not moving house.

987
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:12,230
Why are you bringing so much stuff?

988
00:35:12,230 --> 00:35:14,160
It doesn't hurt to bring a bit more.

989
00:35:14,520 --> 00:35:15,710
There are gifts in here for

990
00:35:15,710 --> 00:35:17,360
Mrs. Chen and the villagers.

991
00:35:18,030 --> 00:35:19,400
Didn't you want to donate books
to No.1 High School?

992
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:20,280
Bring them here.

993
00:35:20,280 --> 00:35:21,140
I'll pack them.

994
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:22,420
I ordered them at the bookstore.

995
00:35:22,420 --> 00:35:23,960
I asked them to deliver them.

996
00:35:23,960 --> 00:35:26,090
I'm not carrying anything that heavy.

997
00:35:27,260 --> 00:35:28,220
It is a bit much.

998
00:35:28,810 --> 00:35:30,230
But the post office is too slow.

999
00:35:30,230 --> 00:35:31,070
We might get home

1000
00:35:31,070 --> 00:35:32,330
before the stuff does.

1001
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:33,680
In the future,

1002
00:35:33,760 --> 00:35:36,020
what you send today can arrive tomorrow.

1003
00:35:36,710 --> 00:35:38,630
You're kidding. How is that possible?

1004
00:35:38,630 --> 00:35:39,830
How is it impossible?

1005
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:40,710
We should always have

1006
00:35:40,710 --> 00:35:41,630
some dreams.

1007
00:35:43,960 --> 00:35:44,440
Mom.

1008
00:35:45,410 --> 00:35:47,370
Did you ask Granny Yu?

1009
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:48,330
What did she say?

1010
00:35:49,150 --> 00:35:50,410
She hasn't agreed yet.

1011
00:35:51,030 --> 00:35:52,480
She has to wait for her son.

1012
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:53,190
She hasn't left this house

1013
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:54,630
for over 10 years,

1014
00:35:54,650 --> 00:35:55,980
and it's New Year's too.

1015
00:35:56,670 --> 00:35:57,840
I can understand that.

1016
00:35:57,840 --> 00:35:59,770
I'm just worried about her health.

1017
00:36:00,510 --> 00:36:00,880
Okay,

1018
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:02,300
I'll go talk to the subdistrict committee.

1019
00:36:02,300 --> 00:36:04,500
I'll ask them to check on her more often.

1020
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:06,880
Have you prepared the gifts
for Zhou Cheng's family?

1021
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:08,080
When do you plan to go?

1022
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:11,210
I'll discuss it with him again.

1023
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:11,760
Mom.

1024
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,960
You and Uncle go back first
the day after tomorrow.

1025
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:15,290
I'll go by myself later.

1026
00:36:15,370 --> 00:36:16,900
No, let's go back together.

1027
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,250
A few days won't matter.

1028
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:19,320
We'll wait for you.

1029
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:20,880
Don't wait. I'm going out of town.

1030
00:36:20,880 --> 00:36:21,550
Just pack.

1031
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:22,710
Okay.

1032
00:36:27,480 --> 00:36:30,160
[Jingcheng]

1033
00:36:48,550 --> 00:36:49,150
Comrade.

1034
00:36:49,190 --> 00:36:50,230
It looks like it's going to snow.

1035
00:36:50,230 --> 00:36:51,290
Are we still going?

1036
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:38,400
Sir.

1037
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:39,370
Let's go.

1038
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:41,080
To the train station.

1039
00:37:41,110 --> 00:37:41,710
All right.

1040
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:49,760
I don't think this woman

1041
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:50,490
and the child

1042
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,300
are related to Zhou Cheng.

1043
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:54,550
But I'm still upset

1044
00:37:54,550 --> 00:37:56,440
that he hid it from me.

1045
00:37:59,030 --> 00:38:01,430
I don't want to
fall into a romantic cliché.

1046
00:38:02,270 --> 00:38:04,270
I'll wait for him to tell me himself.

1047
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:58,450
The skin should be thick, not too thin.

1048
00:38:59,290 --> 00:39:00,480
When you pinch it,

1049
00:39:01,070 --> 00:39:02,400
don't do it too tightly.

1050
00:39:05,190 --> 00:39:05,760
Look.

1051
00:39:06,190 --> 00:39:08,000
Birdcage shape, grain beak.

1052
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:09,050
Pretty, right?

1053
00:39:09,070 --> 00:39:10,760
It's so exquisite.

1054
00:39:12,550 --> 00:39:13,070
Got it?

1055
00:39:13,070 --> 00:39:13,550
Come on, wrap one.

1056
00:39:13,550 --> 00:39:14,320
Let me try.

1057
00:39:15,230 --> 00:39:15,760
Xiaolan.

1058
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:17,680
I'll make one for you too.

1059
00:39:19,880 --> 00:39:20,410
Xiaolan.

1060
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:22,060
Why are you zoning out?

1061
00:39:22,280 --> 00:39:23,030
Look at you.

1062
00:39:23,230 --> 00:39:24,000
Zhou Cheng

1063
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,400
went back to the capital for New Year,

1064
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:27,130
and look at you,
you're already zoning out.

1065
00:39:27,130 --> 00:39:28,770
You two
haven't even registered your marriage yet.

1066
00:39:28,770 --> 00:39:30,190
Auntie, what are you saying?

1067
00:39:30,190 --> 00:39:30,880
Tao is here.

1068
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:34,610
What were you guys talking about just now?

1069
00:39:34,710 --> 00:39:36,040
I didn't hear anything.

1070
00:39:36,800 --> 00:39:37,110
Okay.

1071
00:39:37,110 --> 00:39:37,710
Good that you didn't hear it.

1072
00:39:37,710 --> 00:39:38,510
I'll wrap one too.

1073
00:39:38,510 --> 00:39:39,320
All right.

1074
00:39:40,030 --> 00:39:40,710
Go play.

1075
00:39:41,800 --> 00:39:43,060
We don't need you here.

1076
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:45,800
Fine, I'm being rejected again.

1077
00:39:46,110 --> 00:39:47,040
Comrade Liu Fen.

1078
00:39:47,550 --> 00:39:49,210
How did you convince Granny Yu

1079
00:39:49,250 --> 00:39:50,250
to get her

1080
00:39:50,280 --> 00:39:51,840
to come to our house for New Year?

1081
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:52,550
I was worried

1082
00:39:52,550 --> 00:39:53,480
that after we all came back,

1083
00:39:53,480 --> 00:39:54,510
what if when she was alone

1084
00:39:54,510 --> 00:39:55,550
at home...

1085
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:59,590
Say auspicious things during New Year's.

1086
00:39:59,590 --> 00:40:01,400
What do you mean you're worried about me?

1087
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:03,060
I'm the one worried about you.

1088
00:40:04,080 --> 00:40:05,370
I'm worried your mom

1089
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:06,960
would get bullied by others.

1090
00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:08,190
That's why I came.

1091
00:40:08,590 --> 00:40:10,450
Otherwise, I wouldn't have come.

1092
00:40:11,130 --> 00:40:11,670
That's great.

1093
00:40:11,670 --> 00:40:14,600
Look at all this dried seafood.

1094
00:40:14,630 --> 00:40:16,180
How do we prepare this?

1095
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:18,240
Isn't the head chef here?

1096
00:40:18,590 --> 00:40:20,550
Granny Yu is knowledgeable.

1097
00:40:20,800 --> 00:40:21,800
Things that fly in the sky,

1098
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:23,030
run on the ground, and swim in the sea—

1099
00:40:23,030 --> 00:40:23,920
she knows them all.

1100
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:24,590
Right?

1101
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:26,550
Don't flatter me.

1102
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:28,050
Granny Yu, teach us.

1103
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:29,210
Abalone...

1104
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:31,800
It needs to be soaked in clean water.

1105
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:33,400
Change the water twice a day.

1106
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:35,000
I think it'll be ready to cook

1107
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:36,000
by New Year's Eve.

1108
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:36,480
I see.

1109
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:37,000
All right!

1110
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:38,460
I'll go get a basin of water

1111
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:40,420
to soak the abalone first.

1112
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:43,510
Xiaolan!

1113
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:45,710
Mrs. Chen!

1114
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:47,150
Happy New Year.

1115
00:40:47,150 --> 00:40:49,280
You're getting more and more radiant.

1116
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:51,840
Is Chen Qing coming back this year?

1117
00:40:52,440 --> 00:40:53,400
He can't.

1118
00:40:53,680 --> 00:40:54,590
He insisted on going abroad

1119
00:40:54,590 --> 00:40:55,920
for graduate school.

1120
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:57,230
We don't have to pay

1121
00:40:57,230 --> 00:40:58,540
his tuition,

1122
00:40:58,760 --> 00:41:00,590
but we have to pay for his travel.

1123
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:01,810
It's so far away.

1124
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:03,700
He can't just come back whenever.

1125
00:41:03,970 --> 00:41:05,040
You're better.

1126
00:41:05,070 --> 00:41:06,360
Staying by your mom's side—

1127
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,400
that's being a good daughter.

1128
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:07,960
No.

1129
00:41:07,980 --> 00:41:09,240
Chen Qing is good, too.

1130
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:11,080
Mrs. Chen. Happy New Year.

1131
00:41:11,110 --> 00:41:12,070
You're all back!

1132
00:41:12,070 --> 00:41:13,320
Come, come, have a bite at my place.

1133
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:14,580
We're learning to make

1134
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:15,710
barbecue pork buns.

1135
00:41:15,710 --> 00:41:17,110
The Cantonese love them.

1136
00:41:17,110 --> 00:41:17,590
Come on.

1137
00:41:17,670 --> 00:41:18,270
Oh, right.

1138
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:20,420
Look at the pastries I bought for you.

1139
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:22,130
I queued for a long time!

1140
00:41:22,330 --> 00:41:23,360
You're too kind.

1141
00:41:24,920 --> 00:41:25,760
Where's your mom?

1142
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:26,190
My mom?

1143
00:41:26,370 --> 00:41:26,880
She's inside.

1144
00:41:26,880 --> 00:41:27,680
She's inside.

1145
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:30,320
Great. Let me ask you something.

1146
00:41:30,320 --> 00:41:31,630
Since you're back,

1147
00:41:31,880 --> 00:41:33,550
and the house is renovated...

1148
00:41:34,230 --> 00:41:35,280
It's the New Year.

1149
00:41:35,630 --> 00:41:36,830
You'll definitely be

1150
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:38,510
visiting around the village, right?

1151
00:41:38,510 --> 00:41:39,040
Yes, yes.

1152
00:41:39,360 --> 00:41:40,590
If someone

1153
00:41:41,480 --> 00:41:42,540
wants to introduce

1154
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,530
a partner to your mom

1155
00:41:44,590 --> 00:41:45,790
and have her remarry,

1156
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:47,430
would you agree to it?

1157
00:41:48,110 --> 00:41:49,670
Would I agree to it?

1158
00:41:49,920 --> 00:41:51,320
It doesn't matter if I do.

1159
00:41:51,630 --> 00:41:52,840
It's up to my mom.

1160
00:41:53,510 --> 00:41:54,640
That's for sure!

1161
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:55,590
Mrs. Chen!

1162
00:41:57,340 --> 00:41:58,500
Tao, say hello.

1163
00:41:58,550 --> 00:41:59,510
Hello, Mrs. Chen.

1164
00:41:59,510 --> 00:42:00,760
You've grown so tall.

1165
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:02,480
Come in and sit for a while.

1166
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:03,200
Come on in.

1167
00:42:03,230 --> 00:42:04,860
Liu Fen, you're so beautiful.

1168
00:42:04,860 --> 00:42:06,720
More beautiful than a butterfly.

1169
00:42:07,370 --> 00:42:08,010
Well...

1170
00:42:08,370 --> 00:42:09,370
I... I won't go in.

1171
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:10,710
Since all of you are home.

1172
00:42:10,710 --> 00:42:11,910
Just ask for me, okay?

1173
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:14,070
I'll come another day.

1174
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:15,160
I'm off.

1175
00:42:15,190 --> 00:42:15,920
Take care.

1176
00:42:15,920 --> 00:42:16,630
Goodbye, Mrs. Chen.

1177
00:42:16,630 --> 00:42:18,030
We'll visit you later!

1178
00:42:20,450 --> 00:42:21,040
Fengmei,

1179
00:42:21,070 --> 00:42:21,800
what was it?

1180
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:23,230
Tao.

1181
00:42:23,510 --> 00:42:25,770
Go back to your room and do your homework.

1182
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:27,030
Forget homework. It's New Year's.

1183
00:42:27,030 --> 00:42:29,230
Come soak the abalone with me. Let's go.

1184
00:42:30,320 --> 00:42:31,320
Why did she leave?

1185
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:33,800
She didn't stay
for the barbecue pork buns?

1186
00:42:34,230 --> 00:42:35,070
She...

1187
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:37,360
came to be a matchmaker.

1188
00:42:37,670 --> 00:42:38,470
A matchmaker?

1189
00:42:38,800 --> 00:42:39,670
For whom?

1190
00:42:40,130 --> 00:42:41,650
For Fen.

1191
00:42:43,030 --> 00:42:44,230
Fen, be honest,

1192
00:42:44,670 --> 00:42:45,960
do you want to consider

1193
00:42:46,110 --> 00:42:47,310
finding a companion?

1194
00:42:47,710 --> 00:42:48,190
I...

1195
00:42:48,330 --> 00:42:49,280
What kind of man do you want to find?

1196
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,760
I don't plan to look for anyone else.

1197
00:42:50,760 --> 00:42:51,410
I'm not.

1198
00:42:51,440 --> 00:42:51,840
I mean,

1199
00:42:51,880 --> 00:42:54,230
why would she try to
matchmake at this point of time?

1200
00:42:54,230 --> 00:42:55,170
It's the New Year.

1201
00:42:55,170 --> 00:42:56,900
She's just testing the waters.

1202
00:42:57,120 --> 00:42:58,150
Who knows how many more people

1203
00:42:58,150 --> 00:42:59,800
will come knocking soon.

1204
00:43:00,320 --> 00:43:01,510
You need to figure out

1205
00:43:01,510 --> 00:43:02,570
how to deal with it.

1206
00:43:03,630 --> 00:43:04,550
Come on.

1207
00:43:04,960 --> 00:43:06,690
Let's make barbecue pork buns.

1208
00:43:08,510 --> 00:43:09,400
Let's make buns.

1209
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:10,400
Let's get to it. Hurry up.

1210
00:43:10,400 --> 00:43:11,840
Let's go inside and make buns.
